{
    "info": {
        "name": "Nearby Driver Matching System API",
        "_postman_id": "nearby-driver-api-v1",
        "description": "API for finding nearby available drivers based on pickup location and radius.\n\n**Production URL:** https://nearby-driver-matching-system.vercel.app\n\n**Features:**\n- Find nearby drivers within specified radius\n- Haversine formula for accurate distance calculation\n- Returns drivers sorted by distance (nearest first)\n- Filters only available drivers\n\n**Author:** Md. Mohon\n**GitHub:** https://github.com/Mohon45/nearby-driver",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "base_url",
            "value": "https://nearby-driver-matching-system.vercel.app",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "local_url",
            "value": "http://localhost:5000",
            "type": "string"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Ride Management",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Request Ride - Production",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json",
                                "type": "text"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"user_id\": 1,\n  \"pickup_lat\": 23.8103,\n  \"pickup_lng\": 90.4125,\n  \"radius_km\": 5\n}",
                            "options": {
                                "raw": {
                                    "language": "json"
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/ride/request",
                            "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                            "path": ["api", "ride", "request"]
                        },
                        "description": "Request a ride by providing pickup location and search radius.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `user_id` (number): ID of the user requesting the ride\n- `pickup_lat` (number): Latitude of pickup location\n- `pickup_lng` (number): Longitude of pickup location\n- `radius_km` (number): Search radius in kilometers\n\n**Response:**\n- `success` (boolean): Request status\n- `available_drivers` (array): List of nearby available drivers\n  - `driver_id` (number): Driver's unique ID\n  - `car_model` (string): Car model\n  - `distance_km` (number): Distance from pickup location in km\n  - `location` (object): Driver's current location\n    - `lat` (number): Latitude\n    - `lng` (number): Longitude\n\n**Example Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"available_drivers\": [\n    {\n      \"driver_id\": 1,\n      \"car_model\": \"Toyota Corolla\",\n      \"distance_km\": 0,\n      \"location\": {\n        \"lat\": 23.8103,\n        \"lng\": 90.4125\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
                {
